        "sender_full_name": "Hernan Ibarra",
        "timestamp": 1728246438
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The free magma doesn't satisfy any law, but if we quotient it by a law it might be that we need to interpret it as universally quantified for the quotient, yeah. I'll admit I haven't thought through how the quotient construction should go exactly</p>",
